OL,3,CGrandfather, 69, 'one bite away from
OL,4,Cdeath' in dog attack
OL,6,FA grandfather was one bite away from
OL,7,Flosing his life, after he was attacked
OL,8,Fby what his family think was an XL
OL,9,Fbully dog.
OL,11,FResham Singh from Gravesend, Kent had
OL,12,Fbeen keeping fit by walking every day.
OL,14,FThe 69-year-old was walking on a quiet
OL,15,Fresidential road on 2 July 2024 when a
OL,16,Fdog attacked him from behind and
OL,17,Fdragged him across the street.
OL,19,FPolice were called to the scene on
OL,20,FLinfield Road at around 8:48pm and Mr
OL,21,FSingh was taken to hospital.
