OL,6,FFollowing the attack, they seized a
OL,7,Fdog and a woman was interviewed under
OL,8,Fcaution while investigations continue.
OL,9,FMr Singh still remains in hospital.
OL,11,FOfficial figures show there are more
OL,12,Fthan 57,000 XLs have been given
OL,13,Fexemption certificates since the ban
OL,14,Fon this breed came into force.
OL,16,FHis son wants the person who should
OL,17,Fhave been in charge of that dog - to
OL,18,Ffeel the full force of the law.
