OL,3,CGrandfather, 69, 'one bite away from
OL,4,Cdeath' in dog attack
OL,6,FMr Singh's son, Raj Dhana said: "I've
OL,7,Fnot seen that much blood ever. And so,
OL,8,Fobviously, when it's a parent of yours
OL,9,Fit's very shocking, right, and very
OL,10,Fsaddening.
OL,12,F"This dog bit him in some really
OL,13,Fcrucial areas, you know, including the
OL,14,Fupper thigh, and took huge chunks out
OL,15,Fof his forearm
