OL,3,CGrandfather, 69, 'one bite away from
OL,4,Cdeath' in dog attack
OL,6,F"The ability of that dog, with one
OL,7,Fmore bite, could have taken out a
OL,8,Fpulse. Or with the next bite have gone
OL,9,Ffor his neck, which my dad was trying
OL,10,Fto protect from, he would have been
OL,11,Fone bit away from (death)."
OL,13,FXL bullies are a banned breed, unless
OL,14,Fyou have an exemption certificate, and
OL,15,Fthey must be muzzled in public places.
OL,17,F"This law to register them, isn't good
OL,18,Fenough," Resham's son added.
